  <title>WebKit2.WebView.is_loading</title>
  <synopsis><code mime="text/x-gjs">
WebView.is_loading: Boolean (Read)
  </code></synopsis>
  <p>Whether the <link xref="WebKit2.WebView"/> is currently loading a page. This property becomes
<code>true</code> as soon as a new load operation is requested and before the
<link xref="WebKit2.WebView-load-changed"/> signal is emitted with <link xref="WebKit2.LoadEvent"/>.started and
at that point the active URI is the requested one.
When the load operation finishes the property is set to <code>false</code> before
<link xref="WebKit2.WebView-load-changed"/> is emitted with <link xref="WebKit2.LoadEvent"/>.finished.</p>

</page>
